                  "fill": "$foreground-secondary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": 700,
                  "content": "We support a wide range of platforms including Windows, macOS, Microsoft 365, and Google Workspace. Our team is experienced with diverse environments and can adapt to your specific technology stack.",
